{"tid":653593,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日本中學生改裝擦紙膠","createTime":"2018-05-05T01:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T04:30:58.000Z","uid":2104,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1e630e0df95e5efc8520b78a13a318298c8dba2e","tid":653593,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T01:10:50.000Z","msg":"日本蜻蜓牌 MONO 擦紙膠，陪伴無數人度過學生時期，前陣子還推出了一款考生專用的無文字版本，而引起話題。近日，它又成了日本推特上的熱門討論對象。原來，有位擅長理工的高中生將小小的 MONO 擦紙膠，改造成 MP3 播放器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/085943_8308c5d3fef854612c3790aea0099042.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F085943_8308c5d3fef854612c3790aea0099042.png&h=d0fafbf2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/085944_5c3aee4715c0a9fa4c57baa08e8ce483.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F085944_5c3aee4715c0a9fa4c57baa08e8ce483.png&h=71a987cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前，一名推特用戶名稱為 107 的日本高中生，利用黃金周假期，做了一個偉大的作品，就是這枚特製 MONO 擦子膠。別看它外觀很正常，內部早已被偷天換日，填滿了電路板、microSD 卡插槽等零件，搖身一變成內建喇叭、能播音樂的 MP3 隨身聽。<br />\n<br />\n只要按下包裝上的 M 字母，《光之美少女》主題曲樂音立即流淌而出，讓人不禁大呼「Jack，這真是太神奇了！」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/090204_8e373b1af27ae23a67731e2c14278b47.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F090204_8e373b1af27ae23a67731e2c14278b47.png&h=4a7decbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為何會有將擦紙膠，改造成播放器的想法？根據《ねとらぼ》報導，107 過去曾經購買過僅要 500 日圓的 MP3 播放器，並發揮創意將該播放器分解，並移植進不要的學生記事本當中，開啟他偷天換日的歷程。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote> <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/kukiwakame107/status/854278331411316737?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Ftechorange%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2Fjapanese-high-school-student-maker-mp3-eraser%2F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fkukiwakame107%2Fstatus%2F854278331411316737%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fbuzzorange.com%252Ftechorange%252F2018%252F05%252F04%252Fjapanese-high-school-student-maker-mp3-eraser%252F&d=114ik6w79hlg5qRUsmN1AGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=9db63f6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/kukiwakame107/status/854278331411316737?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Ftechorange%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2Fjapanese-high-school-student-maker-mp3-eraser%2F</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n▲學生記事本 mix 隨身聽。<br />\n<br />\n然後，他心想是否可以藏進更小的東西裡面？於是把歪腦筋動到了擦紙膠身上，在 2017 年 9 月完成了擦紙膠mp3隨身聽的首個作品。你聽，擦紙膠在播著懷念的《庫洛魔法使》主題曲呢！<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote> <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/kukiwakame107/status/911433277998632960?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Ftechorange%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2Fjapanese-high-school-student-maker-mp3-eraser%2F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fkukiwakame107%2Fstatus%2F911433277998632960%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fbuzzorange.com%252Ftechorange%252F2018%252F05%252F04%252Fjapanese-high-school-student-maker-mp3-eraser%252F&d=114ik6w79hlg5qRUsmN1AGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=1651e757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/kukiwakame107/status/911433277998632960?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Ftechorange%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2Fjapanese-high-school-student-maker-mp3-eraser%2F</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n▲2017 年 9 月完成了橡皮擦隨身聽第一版。<br />\n<br />\n而這回推出的是進化版「擦紙膠隨身聽 ver.2」，主要加強了音量強度。過去是直接將播放器與喇叭直接連接，這回則是加入了放大器，以增加音量；並且加入塑膠板等素材，提升強度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/090818_064224484784c347213b20f562965688.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F090818_064224484784c347213b20f562965688.png&h=62f31e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而耳機孔、USB 端口、microSD 卡插槽，也集中在擦紙膠屁股，方便使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/090937_1a2fd3df3b4ac3809630911200a889e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F090937_1a2fd3df3b4ac3809630911200a889e6.png&h=d697e802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正常情況下，從擦紙膠改造成隨身聽的時間約需 5 個小時，製作費用約 1000 日圓，但由於過程不是那麼順遂，失敗了好多次、累積經驗，花了一個禮拜的時間和 3000 日圓才完成。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote> <a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2018/05/04/japanese-high-school-student-maker-mp3-eraser/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Ftechorange%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2Fjapanese-high-school-student-maker-mp3-eraser%2F&d=114ik6w79hlg5qRUsmN1AGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=e27c4593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2018/05/04/japanese-high-school-student-maker-mp3-eraser/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本仔真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ea99b3cf42396e4a699f952bf954f5bccaf6c6","tid":653593,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T01:31:38.000Z","msg":"根住實有人話：<br />\n<em>如果換轉係支那人你地一定笑人無聊</em>"},{"pid":"fc0fc7b958573eab4529271c571181b1b470350e","tid":653593,"uid":15901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"21ea99b3cf42396e4a699f952bf954f5bccaf6c6","tid":653593,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T01:31:38.000Z","msg":"根住實有人話：<br />\n<em>如果換轉係支那人你地一定笑人無聊</em>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T02:15:00.000Z","msg":"支那人識咁做先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831315803dc07510bab00c645a6625b81e650ac8","tid":653593,"uid":18241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"21ea99b3cf42396e4a699f952bf954f5bccaf6c6","tid":653593,"uid"